  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db9\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0ddd 38\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "38 kilos of drug seized from Embilipitiya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A mother and her son were arrested by Ambilipitiya headquarters police along with 38 kilos of heroin hidden in a house in Ambilipitiya city.",
        "The police say that there were 38 kg and 360 grams in this house and they were packed in 36 packages. The police have estimated the street value of this to be over Rs 55 crore.",
        "The suspect's mother is 46 years old and the suspect's son is 22 years old, police said.",
        "The police said that a large-scale drug trafficker in Dubai had sent the drugs, and a relative of the house hid the heroin in this house.",
        "The raid was carried out after a tip-off was received by a soldier of the Police Special Task Force.",
        "The suspect's mother and her child live on rent in this house, and the smuggling has been carried out under the guise of running a business of ready-made clothes and bags, and a digital scale used to measure heroin was also seized from the suspect's bar."
      ],
